{"tid":1961950,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【Zoom爆危機】台行政院點名Zoom存漏洞 下令政府機構禁用","createTime":"2020-04-07T06:34:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T07:36:28.000Z","uid":253992,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4c6ac76f0af90840d8339b36faab39f8845ab0a6","tid":1961950,"uid":253992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T06:34:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.video.appledaily.com/china/20200407/5D6H5PRZAWDIRH3SKJGUSTVCBA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.video.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200407%2F5D6H5PRZAWDIRH3SKJGUSTVCBA%2F&d=oVNa%2F3rGcR5VJv77DJ2lex9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=3412c4de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.video.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200407%2F5D6H5PRZAWDIRH3SKJGUSTVCBA%2F&h=dd3077e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.video.appledaily.com/china/20200407/5D6H5PRZAWDIRH3SKJGUSTVCBA/</a><br />\n武漢肺炎全球大爆發，為減少接觸，不少人在家工作，研發中心設在中國的視像通訊軟件ZOOM大行其道。不過，Zoom被揭發有嚴重安全漏洞，將用戶資料及會議內容都傳到中國，Zoom創辦人袁征隨後承認問題，並公開道歉。不過，台灣行政院今日發出通函，禁止政府機構使用有安全疑慮的產品，包括Zoom，優先使用台灣產品或已獲認證的產品。<br />\n<br />\n行政院資通安全處（以下簡稱「資安處」）今日表示，台灣去年已實施《資通安全管理法》，各政府部門在資訊傳遞及資訊安全安防護上，都要依照相關規定處理、落實，以維護國家安全。資安處指，在各政府機構的系統中，不應使用有安全疑慮的產品，如果需要使用，也應以台灣產品及與政府有共同供應契約的產品優先。<br />\n<br />\n行政院發言人谷辣斯．尤達卡（Kolas Yotaka）昨曾表示，目前行政院進行視像會議，沒有使用Zoom這個軟件，資安處初步統計，各部會也沒有使用。台灣外交部表示，因為Zoom是中國產品，該部沒有使用。<br />\n<br />\n行政院資安處進一步表示，如果情況特殊或需要與國際交流，必須使用非台灣製的視像訊訊軟體，可使用主要國際服務商的軟件。<span style=\"color: red;\">台灣教育部則推薦學校使用Google Meet、Microsoft Teams等軟件，作為向在家學生授課的軟件。<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"5f62216d32faf643f4ac53354b8521b231132b38","tid":1961950,"uid":253992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T06:34:53.000Z","msg":"跟住學校仲要繼續課金用支那Zoom<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdb9e587b374887650fa194a6611a0d83e5db9ee","tid":1961950,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T06:59:37.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"47e4d8fc8a92720aa0f3b0b40f22655ec553b41c","tid":1961950,"uid":123738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T07:20:37.000Z","msg":"支那野就是會爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3c7ab03d99cbb97b4b9caf0c46ea3dd63f70819","tid":1961950,"uid":123192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T07:24:01.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母，個個國家都禁，係戇鳩香港逼學生用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7297f8bfe00b59be50b653ebe68881879a7b104","tid":1961950,"uid":297045,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a3c7ab03d99cbb97b4b9caf0c46ea3dd63f70819","tid":1961950,"uid":123192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T07:24:01.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母，個個國家都禁，係戇鳩香港逼學生用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T07:25:17.000Z","msg":"zoom可以短時間內係香港突然異軍突起 必有古怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d20afe1f3c6dc97922d258f9d6050cafc7f49712","tid":1961950,"uid":9958,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T07:29:27.000Z","msg":"我以為玩野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> google完原來係阿美族人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73d599c2df09c692edd2b87ee809dd0e6af3fe73","tid":1961950,"uid":253992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d20afe1f3c6dc97922d258f9d6050cafc7f49712","tid":1961950,"uid":9958,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T07:29:27.000Z","msg":"我以為玩野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> google完原來係阿美族人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T07:30:52.000Z","msg":"原住民嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de57179cffc8bfa93cb0b08086c1eb